---
import '../styles/global.css';
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>About | Graham Tomori</title>
    </head>

    <body class="font-sans bg-[#cfc6b8] text-[#3b2f2f] flex flex-col min-h-screen">
        <!-- Navbar -->
        <nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 w-full bg-[#3b2f2f] shadow-md z-50">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-white w-full pl-3">
                <!-- Logo + Name + Tagline -->
                <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
                    <img src="/images/stretched-globe-csa-images.png" alt="Globe Logo" class="h-16 w-auto object-contain relative top-0.5" />
                    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
                        <span class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-100">Graham Tomori</span>
                        <span class="text-sm italic text-gray-300">Curiosity in Motion</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Links -->
                <div class="space-x-6 mr-6">
                    <a href="/" class="hover:text-[#c4b78b]">Home</a>
                    <a href="/about" class="hover:text-[#c4b78b] font-bold">About</a>
                    <a href="/projects" class="hover:text-[#c4b78b]">Projects</a>
                    <a href="/resume" class="hover:text-[#c4b78b]">Resume</a>
                    <a href="/contact" class="hover:text-[#c4b78b]">Contact</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <!-- Main About Content -->
        <main class="flex-grow pt-40 pb-24 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold mb-6">About Me</h1>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
                I’m Graham Tomori, a first year student of international business (Simultaneously studying Spanish) at Butler University. I have a passion for
                nation development, rebuilding economies, and designing innovative frameworks for post-conflict recovery. My post-academic goals are to pursue
                governmental consulting, eventually starting my own firm.
            </p>
            <p class="leading-relaxed mb-4">
                This website serves as a public portfolio of my projects, writings, and research. I explore questions of political order, economic development,
                and how nations can transition from instability to sustainable prosperity.
            </p>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
                Beyond academics, I’m also a competitive distance runner, which weighed in heavily on my decision to choose Butler University, as it's ranked as
                a top 15 program in NCAA D1 distance running. I am constantly chasing growth in both athletic and intellectual pursuits, a reflection of my
                personal motto: <span class="italic">Curiosity in Motion</span>.
            </p>
        </main>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <footer class="bg-[#3b2f2f] text-gray-100 py-6 mt-auto">
            <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
                &copy; {year} Graham Tomori. All rights reserved.
            </div>
        </footer>
    </body>
</html>
